	   <tr><td colspan=2>Agility does not affect defensive skills like dodge, parry and riposte.&nbsp;&nbsp;Extensive studies have been performed on these and it has been conclusively determined that they have little to zero effect (within a small margin of error due to random numbers).<br><br>I am performing some tests on damage mitigation of agility AC vs raw AC.  Study should be up soon so I can't say anything conclusive about that.<br><br>Don't believe any of the common myths about stats like that.  Dexterity doesn't do any of those either. :)<br>&nbsp;<br><b>Praetor</b>, 60th Crusader<br>Avatars of Discord</td></tr>
